w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192924\/black-granite-kitchen-sink-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Turn your kitchen sink into a stunning centrepiece<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3<\/strong>. Black Granite Kitchen Countertop for the Win!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A granite slab is a classic choice that suits any kitchen style, from rustic to ultra-modern. Jet black granite or absolute black granite is popular for the uniform colour and durability, making them ideal for busy kitchens.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192911\/black-granite-kitchen-countertop.jpg\" alt=\"A durable black granite kitchen countertop, ideal for busy kitchens\" class=\"wp-image-59076\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192911\/black-granite-kitchen-countertop.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192911\/black-granite-kitchen-countertop-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192911\/black-granite-kitchen-countertop-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192911\/black-granite-kitchen-countertop-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Combine functionality and style<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/black-granite-countertops\/\">Trendy Black Granite Countertops For Your Kitchen<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4<\/strong>. Pack a Punch With a Black Granite Kitchen Trio<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Imagine a kitchen where everything is seamlessly tied together with the bold elegance of black granite. A matching trio consisting of a sleek kitchen island, a stylish sink, and a robust countertop creates a cohesive and luxurious space. This powerful combination enhances the aesthetic appeal and offers unmatched durability, making your kitchen the ultimate showstopper.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192859\/black-granite-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"Sleek black granite kitchen with matching island and sink, exuding luxury and sophistication\" class=\"wp-image-59075\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192859\/black-granite-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192859\/black-granite-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192859\/black-granite-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192859\/black-granite-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A stunning black &#038; beige kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5<\/strong>. Stay Minimal With a Polished Jet-Black Granite Kitchen Platform<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a kitchen platform that is both practical and stylish? We have one for you with a durable work surface that can withstand heavy use while adding an element of elegance. South black granite or jet black granite are excellent choices for this application, offering a smooth finish and consistent colour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192959\/jet-black-granite-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"Jet-black granite kitchen platform, offering a smooth finish and consistent colour\" class=\"wp-image-59080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192959\/jet-black-granite-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192959\/jet-black-granite-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192959\/jet-black-granite-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192959\/jet-black-granite-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A durable kitchen platform should stand the test of time<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End to end interior solutions that save 20% extra space\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/19103933\/end-to-end-interior-solutions-that-save-20-extra-space.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Design a Statement Backsplash With Black Granite<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Why leave the backsplash out when you think of a black granite kitchen? Turn the backsplash into a work of art with black granite. The natural shimmer of granite adds a touch of glamour, especially when paired with under-cabinet lighting. It\u2019s an excellent way to introduce contrast and texture into your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/modular-kitchen-design\/\">kitchen design<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192808\/backsplash-black-granite.jpg\" alt=\"Backsplash with black granite to add a touch of glamour\" class=\"wp-image-59071\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/12192808\/backsplash-black-granite.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads